{"tid":1424361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗係咪一個局!","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:54:27.000Z","uid":291331,"like":87,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"75b0eb4a61d5a52a496501a0612019a2721cbf7c","tid":1424361,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"邊有咁啱5個休班行去啲軍裝平時唔會巡嘅地方<br />\n然後突登拉個有名氣嘅年青人等人又圍<br />\n幾分鐘即刻一架黑警旅遊巴<br />\n有啲人是但著件黑色背心警察兩隻字都無<br />\n明明依家已經好多人走咗仲出嚟做小丑戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最終目的係要黑警每日都起碼出一次,令到市民覺得香港日日亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"3357d86cf89a80ce67bd69a6e90cbe7bf226f8c6","tid":1424361,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90057ce6249dcc0e866ccc3f4f4fd801d1883d7","tid":1424361,"uid":291331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"大家睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c88e634fcf5eb083671b72e84f3137b8531b12","tid":1424361,"uid":291331,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"做場戲等佢地可以出彈"},{"pid":"440ad4d6d2238c5f0c35797b17aad0f44d9f9457","tid":1424361,"uid":264915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"6bbd61c3ea7467aec1fde5d6b34202edcbceb574","tid":1424361,"uid":65390,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"俾料第二日警畜記招<br />\n放大亂局"},{"pid":"1c74d1fc2f76ac2bcd991f4c513d1fb8ce559f20","tid":1424361,"uid":54339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"又中計呀？"},{"pid":"e5383aa912ab68c84ff1d1390fbc150dfea4849d"